				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p202725">Re: UNROM: Reading the current bank number</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=202725#p202725"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Fri Aug 18, 2017 8:29 am&nbsp;</div></td>
